---
name: foreach-child-workflow
version: 1
schema: omhflow/v1
checkpoint:
  stopDeadlineMs: 30000
changePolicy:
  agentsCanPropose: false
  humansCanApprove: true
---
# Foreach Child Workflow

```yaml workflow
stateSchema:
  version: 1
  shape:
    tasks: array
    childRuns: object
foreach:
  id: runChildForTasks
  items: /tasks
  key: /id
  concurrency: 2
  failureMode: allSettled
  output:
    path: /childRuns
  body:
    workflow:
      path: ./foreach-child-worker.omhflow
```
